title: #92Noon! Marney Gellner in for PA! Petersen/Mande/Olsen/Plouffe/Jeffers
description: --Marney Gellner is in for PA! Jim Petersen from Bally Sports checks in, Joe Mande talks life in Hollywood as a Wolves fan, Lea B Olsen talks Lynx and changing norms in youth sports, Trevor Plouffe talks his retirement life and current baseball hot topics, and Ryan Jeffers talks his season so far with the Twins to close.
